                "type": "output_text",
                "text": "### Most recent “What’s new today” story on Microsoft News\n\n- **Title:** *How a single click fueled a global email scam*  \n- **Date:** Mar 4, 2026  \n- **Link:** https://blogs.microsoft.com/on-the-issues/2026/03/04/how-a-global-coalition-disrupted-tycoon/\n\n**Summary:**  \nThe article explains how a phishing-as-a-service operation (“Tycoon 2FA”) enabled cybercriminals to run large-scale email phishing campaigns that could even bypass multi-factor authentication, leading to widespread account takeovers, operational disruption, and data theft. It reports that Microsoft, Europol, and other partners coordinated action to disrupt the infrastructure behind the Tycoon 2FA operation, detailing the coalition effort and the impact of the takedown.",
